          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "r7AnJX",
              "name": "s3t",
              "fill": "#333333",
              "content": "Scene 3: Morning Laundry Space",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "z8HfTh",
              "name": "s3p",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "content": "Prompt: A bright minimal Japanese laundry room scene in the morning, with a compact clothes-drying dehumidifier on caster wheels placed on the tile floor next to a folding clothes drying rack hung with neat rows of white shirts and towels. Soft natural morning light filters through frosted glass, casting gentle shadows. White walls, simple shelving with neatly stacked detergent bottles slightly out of focus, a single small green plant in the corner. Photorealistic, hi-key bright tone, photographed from a 3/4 angle.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Yy8FI",
              "name": "s3j",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "content": "Japanese: 朝のミニマルな脱衣所。タイル床にキャスター付きのコンパクトな衣類乾燥除湿機が置かれ、隣の物干しスタンドに白いシャツやタオルが整然と干されている。すりガラスから柔らかい光、白壁、棚にはボトル類がボケる。明るいトーン、3/4アングル。ロゴ・テキストなし。",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "GVnwA",
              "name": "s3f",
              "fill": "#0066CC",
              "content": "Focus: 「朝×ランドリー空間×清潔感」を演出し、生活感のあるベネフィットを訴求",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            }
          ]
        }
